node.text: This young lady from South Dallas has done remarkable she has risen in the ranks of Hollywood in front of and behind the scenes coming from the absolute hood and rising up in Hollywood,but never forgetting where she’s from… today is your birthday… I have never been more proud of you than I am today and every day!! Happy birthday sis I love you to the moon and back
